{
  "final_answer": "## TJX Q4 FY 2025 Pre-Tax Margin: Beat by 70 BPS\n\n### Details:\n\n**Guidance (provided during Q3 FY 2025 earnings call on November 20, 2024):**\n- Q4 FY 2025 pre-tax profit margin guidance range: **10.8% to 10.9%**\n- High end of guidance: **10.9%**\n\n**Actual Result (reported on February 26, 2025):**\n- Q4 FY 2025 actual pre-tax profit margin: **11.6%**\n\n**Comparison:**\n- 11.6% (actual) − 10.9% (high end of guidance) = **0.70 percentage points**\n- 0.70 percentage points = **70 basis points (BPS)**\n\n### Conclusion:\nTJX **beat** its Q4 FY 2025 pre-tax margin guidance by **70 basis points**. According to the earnings call transcript, this outperformance was \"primarily due to a benefit from lower shrink as well as expense leverage on our above-planned sales, partially offset by higher incentive compensation accruals.\"\n\n### Sources:\n{\n    \"sources\": [\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://www.marketbeat.com/earnings/reports/2024-11-20-the-tjx-companies-inc-stock\",\n            \"name\": \"TJX Companies Q3 2025 Earnings Call Transcript (Q4 Guidance)\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://www.marketbeat.com/earnings/reports/2025-2-26-the-tjx-companies-inc-stock\",\n            \"name\": \"TJX Companies Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://fintool.com/app/research/companies/TJX/earnings/Q4%202025\",\n            \"name\": \"TJX Q4 2025 Earnings Summary - Fintool\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/tjx-companies-inc-tjx-q4-071704796.html\",\n            \"name\": \"TJX Companies Inc (TJX) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Highlights - Yahoo Finance\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://news.futunn.com/en/post/50229181/tjx-companies-tjxus-executives-praised-the-strong-start-to-the\",\n            \"name\": \"TJX Companies Q4 Performance Guidance - Futunn\"\n        }\n    ]\n}",
